Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:02.59,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:05.60,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:07.73,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Stella?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:10.16,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, have you seen Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:11.86,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:13.62,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.94,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Um, about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.67,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's working well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:09.20,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,It absorbs your excess magic and \Nmakes crystal flowers by the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:12.93,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:17.54,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,They're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:18.80,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.74,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:21.92,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Although it looks a bit crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:23.81,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,They look tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:25.37,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:29.93,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,They look tasty to the likes of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.70,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,They do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.89,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Elias, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.66,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Lindel got you dragon castings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:41.77,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,And the fish is from Selkie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.84,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Simon got you a wristwatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.64,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica got you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.69,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she does quick work, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.63,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, can you show me the \Nbracelet you got in Ant Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:56.56,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.58,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:08.06,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you'll be practically \Nunable to absorb or create magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:10.67,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be perfect for your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:15.89,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, don't do any experiments or \Nmagic without my permission, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:17.51,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.51,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.85,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,I can do hardly anything right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.11,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's given me so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.60,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't give anything back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:39.64,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever I can while\Nmy body still moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:44.12,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Elias, I'm going to thank Simon-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:45.77,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:51.55,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you sneaking\N off to London again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:54.66,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I won't go without telling you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.58,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.48,Magus-Internal/narrator,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.75,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.10,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:17.20,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Um, have you seen a boy around?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.74,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.41,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.00,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Stella, come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.63,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:28.83,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.19,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She darted off, saying her \Nbrother's gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.52,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Her brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.53,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She's our only child, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.57,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Elias, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:40.30,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.33,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:51.80,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:55.57,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me find my brother, Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:00.11,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Stella Barklem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:03.38,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I came to my grandma's \Nplace for Christmas break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.38,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Along with my whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:10.52,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I took Ethan to the yard, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:19.07,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,He's frail, but he refused to go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.84,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Then we got in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:28.71,Magus-Flashback,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a selfish little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:46.99,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I told them that Ethan had vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:48.32,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.08,Magus-Flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:55.57,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who remembers my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.58,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:06:01.54,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,They suddenly forgot about their own child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.13,Default,Liquid Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,That's peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.90,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.91,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,How will you compensate us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:12.93,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Compensate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:17.58,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,When we help people, we receive \Nan appropriate payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.10,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.02,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:27.18,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.00,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.37,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.42,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,When I come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.17,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm here at least once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.71,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make {\i1}lots and lots{\i0} of sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.08,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,More than I can carry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.41,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,If it's money you want, I'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:48.68,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,For my whole life, if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:51.76,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.34,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,That will be your payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.79,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:04.57,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.48,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.07,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,A mage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:14.82,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.79,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,A mage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.99,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Technically, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:22.33,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,You must be scared, with all \Nthese weird things happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.21,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:28.60,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not any scarier than \Nnot having my brother back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:30.79,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.85,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.19,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,The dog talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.52,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where he disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.78,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:53.73,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stray away from any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:54.70,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:58.47,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.60,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:01.78,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:04.12,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,We can find you if you get lost, \Nas long as you hold onto that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.54,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.63,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:09.88,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Chise. I'll hold onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.49,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:26.22,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:31.18,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask the neighbors here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:35.21,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if they'll give us \Na straight answer, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.80,Default,Talking Pinecone from Yuru Camp,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.79,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,A Sleigh Beggy is a queen bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:48.27,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,A queen bee gives birth to the children, \Nso the hive takes care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:53.35,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,It's not magic, so it's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:56.67,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a bad negotiation tactic, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:01.30,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where her brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:05.82,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.04,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:09.05,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking to, Chise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.23,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, Stella.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.07,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:15.71,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:57.36,Default,Lanky,0000,0000,0000,,Know... Want...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:04.34,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot... I'm out of flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.52,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, we need details.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.87,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Half a teacup's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.38,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.58,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Chise! Why are you bleeding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.05,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, don't wo—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:29.07,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! How can I {\i1}not{\i0} worry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:30.86,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,What are you even doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.68,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,She's paying her compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.68,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,You're mages, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:38.06,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do it without hurting yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:40.02,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't omnipotent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:46.78,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,I had a brother, too, but \NI can't see him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.06,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to be able to see yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:54.60,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way we can find him for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.89,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I scared you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:03.73,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:10.90,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to your sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.53,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to treat that when we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.30,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:21.74,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Chise. I didn't \Nwant to make you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:25.58,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who suggested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:28.83,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:43.68,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:47.67,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,I should thank you for coming out this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.42,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Ashen Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:53.82,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:58.37,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,I found a young child abandoned in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.84,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Such a pitiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:01.61,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.15,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,He's {\i1}my{\i0} brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.44,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.15,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,What an odd thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:11.47,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,You are the one who \Nabandoned him, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:17.29,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,We hear human words often.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:21.58,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Words and text are sounds \Nand shapes that bear souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:26.84,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Should they reach another, \Nthey cannot be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:28.63,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.35,Magus-Flashback,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a selfish little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:34.93,Magus-Flashback,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.91,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.21,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:46.08,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling what kind of creature \Nwill appreciate the words you spew forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:50.41,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing you didn't tell him to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:54.46,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,You and your brother's bond has been broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.96,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,former older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:02.41,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Can you remember your dear brother's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:06.91,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Stella?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.89,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,It's *****, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:10.80,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.51,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:18.23,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means for a bond to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.74,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,To forget his name, his age, where \Nhe's from, his face, his voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:26.20,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,and whether he even existed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.49,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.42,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:31.75,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Stella!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.88,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,This is mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:44.23,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Can you pay the appropriate \Ncompensation, have-not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:50.57,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's play a game, have-not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:51.57,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.97,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Join us, child of the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:58.56,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Elias!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:07.72,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:14.45,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,You two shall find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:19.40,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give you until sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:23.67,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,If you can find them before that, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.21,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, they're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.99,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,We're at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.94,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,You don't lose anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.50,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,This is too selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.93,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:40.22,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Search frantically for them,\Nwith that beastly nose of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.42,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,The days are short in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:54.68,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:57.66,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to forget him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:06.90,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.73,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:10.92,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:11.77,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:16.22,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the far east. \NHe's from the far west.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.75,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you managed to find each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.56,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to miss\N him on this tiny hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.29,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Elias...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.88,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,You're his older sister, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.12,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,You should believe in \Nyourself and your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:32.19,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,If you care about him enough that it makes\Nyou cry, you won't lose your bond so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.35,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's family or anything else, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:36.96,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.46,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Chise...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:45.82,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.27,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.62,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth, can you track their scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.52,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,They're hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.94,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,It's really faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:58.26,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:04.57,Magus-Flashback,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,With that beastly nose of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.02,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.36,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.30,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth, take care of Stella for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:12.59,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.65,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really safe to use that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:19.63,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,My place has already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:23.54,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,We've been locked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.30,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,I can hardly move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.26,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,I hate old creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:30.35,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,They're too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:34.05,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,And Chise can't use her magic right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.80,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.60,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:45.06,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.02,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,It talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:49.40,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.57,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.91,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.33,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Is this bone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:58.52,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:16:59.73,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Are you wearing a skull?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:01.01,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Does it come off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:02.27,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it your actual skull?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:03.51,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.75,Magus-Internal/narrator,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to react.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:05.75,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.64,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.40,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,You turned human!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:19.46,Default,Haku-ish,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember your sister's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:20.10,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.69,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.33,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:29.19,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:30.51,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:37.08,Default,Haku-ish,0000,0000,0000,,You said you don't need your \Nnagging sister, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.02,Default,Haku-ish,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really not need her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:43.60,Default,Haku-ish,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't family important?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:46.01,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't being serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:50.34,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:56.58,Default,Haku-ish,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand \Nfamilies or marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:02.11,Default,Haku-ish,0000,0000,0000,,Would I understand those emotions \Nif I had blood relatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:06.29,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thought about whether \Nwe're related by blood or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:09.68,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Family is family, either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:15.01,Default,Haku-ish,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a unit, a group of people who cohabitate \Nand help each other out for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:19.32,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like it could be anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:25.08,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I think I really want to \Ntell my sister I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.33,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I want to party with her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:30.84,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it to be anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:36.75,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's what family is. \NPeople that make you feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.89,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Find them! Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.01,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Capture their scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.31,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Find...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.75,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Find what belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:58.81,Default,Haku-ish,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:08.24,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Elias!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:11.94,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Elias!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.53,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness, I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.28,Default,Haku-ish,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:21.63,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Elias...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:27.10,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:31.26,Default,Haku-ish,0000,0000,0000,,A child's curiosity is terrifyingly powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:37.16,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.39,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:42.15,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I said, we're going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:43.65,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:47.19,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want a brother like me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.95,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Does it suck having me as your big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.12,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind having a kid \Nbrother, as long as it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:04.58,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I know of any \Nother brothers, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:16.30,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay with you being my older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:25.58,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you {\i1}want{\i0} me being \Nyour older sister, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:31.38,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember his name now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:32.48,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:35.03,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap, my clothes aren't wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:37.25,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain not to be able to say his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.21,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:45.16,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,That was a fun loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.72,Default,Diablo,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:50.55,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:53.85,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to watch people when they're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:58.29,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,A person's words are powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:02.13,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we stay nearby to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.33,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind, have-not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:09.87,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have what bond you've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.07,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:12.66,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.08,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,you do have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:22.58,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,This looks tastier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:24.50,Default,Journey,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:31.31,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,He was messing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:43.54,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Stella! Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:45.16,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.41,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:47.60,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:50.58,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:52.66,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.28,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:56.63,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Her name's Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:58.69,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,She's my new friend I met today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:02.49,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:04.17,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:05.96,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:08.78,Default,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Stella's so pushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.78,0:22:09.93,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:24:00.07,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,The girl's first friend \Nmakes her heart dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.07,0:24:07.37,Default,Cheats,0000,0000,0000,,But the existence of her friend slightly \Nwarps her relationship with the mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:09.38,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, where are you?!
